title: FRIDAY - Rams dominate SB rematch 2020
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Rams dominate SB rematch 2020
description:
Thursday night saw a rematch of Super Bowl LIII (0:11) as the Rams handled the Patriots behind rookie running back Cam Akers. Wide receiver Cooper Kupp invoking a classic soundbite in his postgame press conference (0:50). We have the latest injury updates on Christian McCaffrey (1:25), Daniel Jones (1:41) and Mike Evans (1:55). We'll preview Monday night's matchup between the Ravens and Browns (2:19) and hear from Baltimore QB Lamar Jackson (2:44) Plus, a couple big-time guests on today's episode Good Morning Football (3:41)
